titles.title: He Is Able To Do Exceeding

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
He is able to do exceeding
Abundantly above all We ask or think
He is able to do exceeding
Abundantly above all We ask or think

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
According to the power That worketh in us
According to the power That worketh in us
He is able to do exceeding Abundantly
Above all we ask or think
